## Explanation

**Test Case 1:**

We can reverse the substring "bab" to make the string "abba" a palindrome.

**Test Case 2:**

The string is already a palindrome.

## Solution

```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int t;
    cin >> t;
    while (t--) {
        int n;
        cin >> n;
        string s;
        cin >> s;
        int ans = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {
            if (s[i] != s[n - i - 1]) {
                ans++;
            }
        }
        cout << ans << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
